OL,3,CDrug dealer tracked down by drone
OL,4,Cafter escaping through roof skylight
OL,6,FA drug dealer has been jailed for more
OL,7,Fthan two years after he was caught
OL,8,Fthanks to a police drone.
OL,10,FJohnny Cafferkey, 26 and of Gloucester
OL,11,FRoad in Avonmouth, tried to escape a
OL,12,Fproperty after police executed a
OL,13,Fwarrant at his address.
OL,15,FHe climbed through a skylight before
OL,16,Fdropping down onto the roof and
OL,17,Fcrawling through brambles next to the
OL,18,Fadjacent railway line.
