OL,3,CDrug dealer tracked down by drone
OL,4,Cafter escaping through roof skylight
OL,6,FOfficers from the South West Regional
OL,7,FOrganised Crime Unit (SWROCU) used a
OL,8,Fdrone to track his movements and he
OL,9,Fwas found near a wheelie bin.
OL,11,FHe was arrested in December 2023 and
OL,12,Fpleaded guilty to the charge of
OL,13,Fpossession with intent to supply class
OL,14,FA and B drugs
OL,16,FCafferkey was handed a 28-month prison
OL,17,Fsentence on 1 February.
