OL,6,FPS Stuart Cumine of SWROCU said:
OL,7,F"Thanks to some excellent partnership
OL,8,Fworking, we were able to apprehend
OL,9,FCafferkey and bring him before the
OL,10,Fcourt.
OL,12,F"I hope the sentence handed to him
OL,13,Fdemonstrates to others that the supply
OL,14,Fof dangerous drugs, in this case
OL,15,Fcocaine and ketamine, is taken
OL,16,Fseriously and will be dealt with
OL,17,Fstrongly."
