OL,6,FSgt Colin Powell, Avon and Somerset
OL,7,FPolice drone unit manager, said:
OL,8,F"Cafferkey thought he could escape
OL,9,Fundetected but what he didn't realise
OL,10,Fwas that we had eyes in the sky
OL,11,Ftracking his every move.
OL,13,F"This is a great example of how
OL,14,Ftechnology can help us catch offenders
OL,15,Fand ensure they are held accountable
OL,16,Ffor their crimes.
